HEADWORD: Feoff
<hw>Feoff</hw> <pr>(?; 277)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <vmorph>[<pos>imp. &
p. p.</pos> <conjf>Feoffed</conjf> <pr>(#)</pr>; <pos>p. pr. & vb.
n.</pos>. <conjf>Feoffing</conjf>.]</vmorph> <ety>[OE.
<ets>feffen</ets>, OF. <ets>feffer</ets>, <ets>fieffer</ets>, F.
